(159, 'Sub 5.1 ', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<strong style=\"text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong style=\"text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong><strong style=\"text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">LANGKAH 5 - PELAKSANAAN &amp; EVALUASI</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.5in; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">5.1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">TABEL PELAKSANAAN PERBAIKAN</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #0070c0;\">Penjelasan pelaksanaan solusi / perubahan yang menggambarkan perbandingan antara rencana dan realisasi pelaksanaan</span></span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;\">Bila solusi / perubahan yang dilakukan merupakan inisiatif replikasi maka dijelaskan pelaksanaan yang melibatkan pihak innovator atau fungsi owner-nya</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;\">Dapat menggunakan tools yang relevan sesuai dengan yang digunakan pada langkah-4 (contoh: Time Line dengan bobot/ S-Curve/ Microsoft Project, dll)</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;\">Lengkapi dengan data monitoring minimal </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: red;\">3 bulan</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #0070c0;\">setelah implementasi termasuk gambar dan data pendukung lainnya serta penjelasan mengenai realisasi biaya terkait solusi / perubahan yang dilakukan&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: .75in; mso-add-space: auto;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif